—ЩLarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/commands/docs/hide.mdЩ@e4313ecdbad370393af59fca88b98a5dd3c3a83f8ed64832122e1059497a5e57«title: hide‘ЁExamplesЩѕHide the alias just defined.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> alias lll = ls -l; hide lll


