’ђђЩйTitle: title: hide
Path: Examples
Content:
Hide the alias just defined.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> alias lll = ls -l; hide lll


```
Hide a custom command.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> def say-hi [] { echo 'Hi!' }; hide say-hi


```
