https://www.nushell.sh/book/thinking_in_nu.html
’ђђЩШTitle: title: hide
Path: Notes
Content:
Definitions are hidden by priority: First aliases, then custom commands.
This command is a parser keyword. For details, check:

https://www.nushell.sh/book/thinking_in_nu.html
